# Financial Risk Capital Adequacy Perpetual Mandatory Preference Shares Amount

## identifier
de7720

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of paid up perpetual cumulative mandatory preference shares on issue by the reporting party.

This item is calculated for capital adequacy purposes and is to be determined in accordance with relevant Prudential Standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.CapitalAdequacy.PerpetualMandatoryPreferenceShares.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
